      <div class="blogBox">
        <h3><a href="http://blog.caixin.com/">财新博客</a></h3>
        <div class="stutitXwen">
          
 <dl>
  <dt>
   <div class="pic">
    <a href="http://ganli.blog.caixin.com/"><img src="http://ucenter.caixin.com/avatar.php?uid=700175&size=small" alt="甘犁" /></a>
   </div>
   <div class="txt">
    <h4><a href="http://ganli.blog.caixin.com/archives/56475" title="保障农民农地权益是新型城镇化的关键">保障农民农地权益是新型城镇化的关键</a></h4>
    <span><a href="http://ganli.blog.caixin.com/archives/comment/56475" class="comments">评论(<em aid="2" tid="56475">0</em>)</a> 05月10日</span>
   </div>
  </dt>
  <dd>
